### Create Item
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "18th Century Writing Desk",
  "base_cost": 5000,
  "age_category": "antique",
  "documents_count": 0
}

### Add Provenance Event 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/1/provenance/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Refinished mahogany surface",
  "year": 1995,
  "event_type": "restoration",
  "documented": true
}

### Add Provenance Event 2
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/1/provenance/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Replaced brass hardware",
  "year": 2005,
  "event_type": "restoration",
  "documented": true
}

### Add Provenance Event 3
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/1/provenance/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Professional appraisal and authentication",
  "year": 2023,
  "event_type": "appraisal",
  "documented": true
}

### Get Item with Provenance
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/1

### Get Valuation
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/1/valuation/

### List all Items
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/items/